---
import Layout from "@layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service">
  <section class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="mb-4">
      Welcome to the G1 Navy website. At G1 Navy, we are committed to protecting
      the privacy of all visitors to our site. We place great importance on
      maintaining the confidentiality and security of personal information, and
      our policy on collecting and using such information is detailed below.
    </p>

    <!-- Personal Information Section -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Personal Information</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      G1 Navy does not require you to provide personal information to access the
      majority of our web pages. However, we do collect personal data on a
      voluntary basis when visitors choose to provide it. This information may
      include your name, job title, company, address, telephone number, email
      address, and other relevant details. Any questions or comments you submit
      may also be treated as personal information.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      The personal information collected is used for various business purposes,
      such as:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
      <li>
        Enabling you to download product details, place orders, and utilize
        specific features of our website.
      </li>
      <li>
        Providing information or interactive services through the website,
        either via email or postal mail, as per your preference.
      </li>
      <li>
        Seeking your feedback on our products and services or communicating with
        you about those services offered on our website.
      </li>
      <li>Processing orders or applications you submit to us.</li>
      <li>
        Managing or fulfilling any contractual obligations we have with you.
      </li>
      <li>
        Identifying and resolving any issues with products or services you may
        experience.
      </li>
      <li>Developing products or services tailored to your needs.</li>
      <li>
        Improving our operations, responding to your inquiries, and sharing
        information about our offerings.
      </li>
      <li>Facilitating your subscription to our newsletter.</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mb-4">
      G1 Navy does not use or share the information collected on this page for
      direct marketing purposes, either internally or with third parties.
      However, we may transfer this information to other countries, including
      among our affiliates, for purposes like storage and the processing
      activities outlined above.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      In compliance with legal requirements, we may also collect, use, and
      disclose personal information during security investigations, cooperation
      with law enforcement, or for other legal purposes.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      We may also anonymize your personal information and use the remaining data
      for historical, statistical, or research purposes.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      By contacting us via email, you are voluntarily providing us with your
      information. Your email address will only be used to respond to your
      queries and will not be utilized for unsolicited mass mailing.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      By accessing our website, you agree to the terms outlined in this privacy
      policy and consent to the continued use of any previously collected
      information. By submitting personal information to us, you authorize G1
      Navy to process your data according to the terms of this policy.
    </p>

    <!-- Non-Personal Information Section -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Non-Personal Information</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      Our website may automatically collect certain data sent by your web
      browser. This data might include your domain name, IP address, operating
      system and platform, the average time spent on our website, pages viewed,
      search terms, and other relevant statistics.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      Such information is used solely to enhance the functionality of our
      website and provide a better service to visitors. We may share aggregated
      data about website usage with the owners or operators of third-party
      websites that link to our site. This data will not contain personally
      identifiable information.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      We use this data to understand how visitors navigate our site, which pages
      are of most interest, and to identify areas for improvement.
    </p>

    <!-- Information Placed on Your Computer Section -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">
      Cookies and Similar Technologies
    </h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      G1 Navy may place cookies or similar technologies on your computer to
      enhance your experience on our website. These small files store
      information that can make your future visits easier by saving your
      preferences and login details.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      You can choose to delete or block these files through your browser
      settings. Please note that doing so may limit the functionality available
      to you on our website. The information stored in these files helps us
      personalize your experience, allow auto-completion of forms, and make
      ongoing improvements to better serve you.
    </p>

    <!-- Security Section -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">
      Security of Your Information
    </h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      We implement advanced security measures to protect your personal
      information from unauthorized access and misuse. These measures are
      regularly reviewed and updated to ensure your privacy is always protected.
    </p>

    <!-- Third Parties Section -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">
      Links to Third-Party Websites
    </h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      Our website may contain links to other websites, including those owned by
      G1 Navy or external entities. We are not responsible for the privacy
      practices or the content of such websites. We recommend reviewing the
      privacy policies of any third-party sites you visit.
    </p>

    <!-- Contacting Us Section -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Contacting Us</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      If you have any questions or wish to review or modify the personal
      information you have provided, please contact us at <a
        href="mailto:info@g-1.tech"
        class="text-blue-600 underline"
        >business@g-1.tech
      </a>. If you have concerns about our use of your personal information,
      please email us with the subject line "Privacy Inquiry."
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      We strive to maintain accurate and up-to-date records of the information
      you provide to us. Please reach out to us with any updates or corrections.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
